{
  "id": "guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale",
  "title": "Format data based on locale",
  "contents": "\n\n\n<div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/aio/aio/content/guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供编辑建议\" title=\"提供编辑建议\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"format-data-based-on-locale\" translation-result=\"on\">根据语言环境格式化数据<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#format-data-based-on-locale\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1><h1 translation-origin=\"off\" id=\"format-data-based-on-locale\">Format data based on locale<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#format-data-based-on-locale\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n<a id=\"i18n-pipes\"></a>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">Angular 提供了以下内置的数据转换<a href=\"guide/glossary#pipe\" title=\"pipe - Glossary | Angular\">管道</a>。数据转换管道会使用 <a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" title=\"LOCALE_ID | Core - API | Angular\"><code>LOCALE_ID</code></a> 标记来根据每个语言环境的规则来格式化数据。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Angular provides the following built-in data transformation <a href=\"guide/glossary#pipe\" title=\"pipe - Glossary | Angular\">pipes</a>. The data transformation pipes use the <a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" title=\"LOCALE_ID | Core - API | Angular\"><code>LOCALE_ID</code></a> token to format data based on rules of each locale.</p>\n\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"api/common/DatePipe\" title=\"DatePipe | Common - API | Angular\"> <code>DatePipe</code> </a>：格式化日期值。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"api/common/DatePipe\" title=\"DatePipe | Common - API | Angular\"><code>DatePipe</code></a>: Formats a date value.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" title=\"CurrencyPipe | Common - API | Angular\"> <code>CurrencyPipe</code> </a>：将数字转换为货币字符串。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" title=\"CurrencyPipe | Common - API | Angular\"><code>CurrencyPipe</code></a>: Transforms a number to a currency string.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"api/common/DecimalPipe\" title=\"DecimalPipe | Common - API | Angular\"> <code>DecimalPipe</code> </a>：将数字转换为十进制数字字符串。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"api/common/DecimalPipe\" title=\"DecimalPipe | Common - API | Angular\"><code>DecimalPipe</code></a>: Transforms a number into a decimal number string.</p>\n\n</li>\n<li>\n<p translation-result=\"on\"><a href=\"api/common/PercentPipe\" title=\"PercentPipe | Common - API | Angular\"> <code>PercentPipe</code> </a>：将数字转换为百分比字符串。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\"><a href=\"api/common/PercentPipe\" title=\"PercentPipe | Common - API | Angular\"><code>PercentPipe</code></a>: Transforms a number to a percentage string.</p>\n\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p translation-result=\"on\">例如， <code>{{today | <a href=\"api/common/DatePipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">date</a>}}</code> 会使用 <code><a href=\"api/common/DatePipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">DatePipe</a></code> 以 <code><a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a></code> 中语言环境的格式显示当前日期。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">For example, <code>{{today | <a href=\"api/common/DatePipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">date</a>}}</code> uses <code><a href=\"api/common/DatePipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">DatePipe</a></code> to display the current date in the format for the locale in <code><a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a></code>.</p>\n\n<p translation-result=\"on\">要覆盖 <code><a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a></code> 的值，请添加 <code>locale</code> 参数。例如，无论你为 <code><a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a></code> 设置哪种语言语言环境，要强制货币使用 <code>en-US</code> ，请使用以下形式： <code>{{amount | <a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">currency</a> : 'en-US'}}</code> 。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">To override the value of <code><a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a></code>, add the <code>locale</code> parameter. For example, to force the currency to use <code>en-US</code> no matter which language-locale you set for <code><a href=\"api/core/LOCALE_ID\" class=\"code-anchor\">LOCALE_ID</a></code>, use this form: <code>{{amount | <a href=\"api/common/CurrencyPipe\" class=\"code-anchor\">currency</a> : 'en-US'}}</code>.</p>\n\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最后复查时间： 2021/9/15</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - api/common/DatePipe\n - api/common/getLocaleExtraDayPeriodRules\n - api/common/getLocaleExtraDayPeriods\n - api/common/registerLocaleData\n - guide/i18n-common\n - guide/pipes\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/common/CurrencyPipe\n - api/common/DatePipe\n - api/common/DecimalPipe\n - api/common/PercentPipe\n - api/core/LOCALE_ID\n - guide/glossary#pipe\n - guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale#format-data-based-on-locale\n - https://github.com/ng-docs/angular-cn/edit/aio/aio/content/guide/i18n-common-format-data-locale.md?message=docs%3A%20请简述你的修改...\n-->"
}